{"tid":402295,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲男鬼屋遊玩後死亡　海洋公園：非常悲痛","createTime":"2017-09-16T10:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T09:54:52.000Z","uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"592b1a923eca32abde75f7c8446d3895f0351760","tid":402295,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"一名21歲男子下午在海洋公園玩「鬼屋」期間昏迷，送院後證實不治。事後園方已將有關遊戲關閉。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園行政總裁李繩宗證實，死者姓張，下午2時左右，進入名為「活埋凶間」的遊戲後大約5分鐘，被發現在工作人員工作的「後勤設施」位置昏迷，工作人員馬上通知醫療團隊到場，並召喚救護車將男子送院。<br />\n<br />\n他說，對意外感到非常悲痛，園方正調查事故原因，亦會配合機電工程署的調查。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園演藝節目總監歐陽綺華表示，有關遊戲設施是一條滑梯，已獲機電署批准，園方每天亦有進行檢查工作。她又以事件已進入調查階段為由，拒絕透露有關遊戲的設計和安全性等問題。<br />\n<br />\n機電工程署表示，已派員到公園了解，調查事發原因。"},{"pid":"1fbb0042cb6689c7fc126beb665136b780a85a74","tid":402295,"uid":9932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ab6f18b408b5f7b29e165c4d803f2b9bb4cf58","tid":402295,"uid":30055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"今次真係真鬼假鬼難分了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50d55d18772a91f2e88b979fbd54e595bf95836","tid":402295,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:34:06.000Z","msg":"真係有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6507f1a4514850c99c8f436d77603ad0bd660a5","tid":402295,"uid":3818,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔嚇得就咪入場啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37780542bc87ff9bca16cd8a5d7faad764622ffa","tid":402295,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma